list.abstract: Swing（英 [swɪŋ]，美 [swɪŋ]），英语单词，作动词为摆动；摇动；纵身一跳。作名词为秋千；摇动；意见的明显变化。短语搭配有in full swing（在热烈进行中，处于兴盛阶段，活动高潮期）。例句为“Bella didn't get off the swing.（贝拉没有从秋千上下来。）” Swing相关近义词有bob、ricketiness等。
Swing是一个用于开发Java应用程序用户界面的开发工具包。它以抽象窗口工具包（AWT）为基础使跨平台应用程序可以使用任何可插拔的外观风格。Swing开发人员只用很少的代码就可以利用Swing丰富、灵活的功能和模块化组件来创建优雅的用户界面。工具包中所有的包都是以swing作为名称，例如javax.swing、javax.swing.event等。

yingyinNormal.en: Don't forget the swing. Don't worry, Peppa. We won't.
yingyinNormal.zh: 别忘了搭一个秋千！放心吧，佩奇。不会忘的。

yingyinNormal.en: Don't forget the swing. Don't worry, Peppa. We won't.
yingyinNormal.zh: 别忘了搭一个秋千！放心吧，佩奇。不会忘的。

yingyinNormal.en: Look, I could swing around that neutron star to decelerate.
yingyinNormal.zh: 听着，我可以利用那颗中子星来抵消黑洞的引力。

yingyinNormal.en: Yeah, now Whittaker's gonna focus on swing states, fundraising...
yingyinNormal.zh: 惠特克会关注摇摆州，筹款……

yingyinNormal.en: Me too! Let's play on the swing. Here is Pedro Pony on the swing. Pedro, can I have a go now? I just want to swing a bit more.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我也是！我们还是去玩秋千吧。小马佩德罗在秋千上玩呢。佩德罗，现在能让我玩吗？可我还想在秋千上再多玩一会呢。

yingyinNormal.en: Roll up, roll up. For the vegetable roundabout swing things. A vegetable roundabout swing thing.
yingyinNormal.zh: 摇起来，转起来！各位小朋友都快来坐蔬菜转专椅。来吧！可以坐蔬菜转转椅咯！

yingyinNormal.en: And that's great for you guys, but we want a lawn and a swing set.
yingyinNormal.zh: 对你们来说这没什么问题，但是我们想要一个草坪和秋千。

yingyinNormal.en: Who? Cathy Durant. Now, Louisiana's not a swing state, I know that.
yingyinNormal.zh: 谁？凯茜·杜兰特，路易斯安那不是摇摆州，这我清楚。

yingyinNormal.en: George is a bit too little for the roundabout. He is playing on the swing.
yingyinNormal.zh: 乔治还太小不能玩旋转圆盘。他就在荡秋千。

yingyinNormal.en: But wait. It's not finished. What? You forgot the swing. Oh, no. We didn't.
yingyinNormal.zh: 等一下！还没有全部完工呢。什么？你们忘了秋千了。哞！不，我们没有忘。

yingyinNormal.en: All right, if you must know, I had a traumatic swing incident when I was little.
yingyinNormal.zh: 好吧，如果你想知道我小时候荡秋千遇险真的?

yingyinNormal.en: I'm the swing vote. My seat is important. You can make a lasting difference here.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我是决定性一票，我的位置很重要。你在这里可以产生长期的影响。

yingyinNormal.en: You can't lift a hammer. You can't swing an axe. You can't even throw one of these!
yingyinNormal.zh: 你举不起榔头又挥不动斧头，连这玩意都不会丢。

yingyinNormal.en: Very good. But wait. It's not finished. What? You forgot the swing. Oh, no. We didn't.
yingyinNormal.zh: 非常好。等一下！还没有全部完工呢。什么？你们忘了秋千了。哞！不，我们没有忘。

yingyinNormal.en: Look, I'm really sorry, but this date is unbreakable. Maybe we can swing by later or something.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我真的很抱歉，但是这个约会是非去不可的，也许我们能晚些碰头，或者…

yingyinNormal.en: Come on, don't go to school. Girls' day! We'll swing by the mall. You could use a new everything.
yingyinNormal.zh: 拜托，别去学校了。姐妹日！我们一起去逛商场，你可以把全身衣物都换新的。

yingyinNormal.en: I know. I almost called off my wedding. Oh, who's your band? Oh, my fiancee wants the Swing Kings.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我知道，我差点取消了婚礼，你请了哪个乐团？我未婚夫想请摇摆国王。

yingyinNormal.en: I was 4 years old. And I was on the swing and then all of a sudden my hair got tangled in the chain.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我四岁荡秋千时，突然头发缠到铁链。

yingyinNormal.en: They also don't care for it if you stare at them and hyperventilate. Sadly, that's my home run swing.
yingyinNormal.zh: 她们也不关心，你是不是盯着她们呼吸加速，挺惨的，在我们家这就像是家族传统。

yingyinNormal.en: Honey, it's gonna be okay. No. No it's not. It's not gonna be okay. It sucks. No swing band. No lilies.
yingyinNormal.zh: 亲爱的，没关系的。不，有关系。没有乐团，没有百合。那很好啊。

examination_example.sentence: With or without a club or racket, <highlight>swing</highlight> like you're hitting the ball.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 不管有没有球杆或球拍，都要像击球一样挥拍。

disambiguation_list.sense_disambiguation: “摆动”，多指物体上端固定，下端摆来摆去。
“振动、颤动”，指短时间内剧烈地摇动，其对象为有形的、具体的物质。
“波动”，指无形的东西，如水平、特性、价格等。
“挥动、飘动”，指有形的东西，如“旗帜、树枝”等。
意为“摆动”，即上端固定，下端摇动。
指意为“晃动”，即下端固定，上端摇动。

examination_example.sentence_trans: 贝拉没有从秋千上下来。

examination_example.sentence: Molly counted to 100 while Bella was on the <highlight>swing</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 贝拉荡秋千时，莫莉数到100。

examination_example.sentence: John suddenly jumped off the <highlight>swing</highlight> without even slowing down.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 约翰突然从秋千上跳下来，甚至没有减速。

examination_example.sentence: "Huh, that s easy." said Melissa—and <highlight>swung</highlight> herself quickly to the top.
examination_example.sentence_trans: “嗯，那很简单。”梅丽莎说——然后迅速荡到了顶点。

examination_example.sentence: One day, our teacher had each of us race across the monkey bars (攀爬架), <highlight>swinging</highlight> from one rung (横杠) to the next.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 一天，我们的老师让我们每个人跑过单杠，从一个横档荡到下一个横档。

examination_example.sentence: There he will stand <highlight>swinging</highlight> his ears, to drive away the flies.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 他会站在那里摆动他的耳朵，赶走苍蝇。
